kdl.prox.qgraph2
Class QGConstraint

java.lang.Object
  kdl.prox.qgraph2.QGConstraint
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, AbsQueryChild
public class QGConstraint
extends java.lang.Object
implements AbsQueryChild, java.io.Serializable

Represents one constraint from the list of possibly many constraints in a QGQuery. QGConstraintS are created for every <test> element in the <constraint> section of a query. <test> elements are connected by <and>S. When processing a query, the transformations that apply a constraint do their work and then remove the constraint from the list of constraints in the Query object.
